es.deusto.serialization

Class UserInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.deusto.serialization.GenericUserInfo
      • es.deusto.serialization.UserInfo

  • public class UserInfo
extends GenericUserInfo
    All the ...Info classes work as a middleman for the client and server bussines objects. Due to the functionality of this classes their structure is similar to the 'original' ones in the server Examples: UserInfo: User EventInfo: Event Also the ...Info clases are the ones shown in the GUI.
